{"word":"συντρέφω","slug":"συντρέφω","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<el><b>συντρέφω</b></el> <el>(<a href='S:future tense'>fut.</a> <el>-θρέψω</el>) </el><p/><div class='li500'><b>I. </b><i>to feed together</i> or <i>besides</i>, <b><a href='S:Xenophon'>Xen.</a></b><p/></div><div class='li500'><b>II. </b><a href='S:passive signification'><a href='S:Passive Voice'>Pass.</a></a> <i>to grow up together</i>, <b><a href='S:Xenophon'>Xen.</a></b>; <el>τινι</el> <i>with</i> one, <b><a href='S:Euripides'>Eur.</a></b><p/></div><div class='li750'><b>2. </b>of feelings or sentiments, <i>to grow up with</i>, <b><a href='S:Aristotle'>Arist.</a></b>, <b><a href='S:Plutarch'>Plut.</a></b>: <i>to be organised</i>, of bodies, <b><a href='S:Plato'>Plat.</a></b><p/></div>"}]}